  <p>Applying online will speed up the appeals process.</p>
  <p>If you cannot use the online service, contact the Planning Inspectorate customer support team on 0303 444 5000, or email: <a href="mailto:enquiries@planninginspectorate.gov.uk">enquiries@planninginspectorate.gov.uk</a>.</p>

